<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        Eberspachs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und auch in
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> brief meldt, wie ewch
                                <expan>fürkom<ex>m</ex></expan>, daz die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>kawfflewt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>reit<ex>en</ex></expan> und geleyten auf der strasse etc., also
                                <expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan> wir zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlin, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden; und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im das <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
